        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 17-20. Sierracapnia shepardi. Male: 17. Parker Creek, California. Genitalia, dorsal, epiproct and knob on tergum 7. 18. South Fork Yuba River, California. Genitalia, lateral, epiproct and knobs on tergum 9. 19. Parker Creek, California. Knob on tergum 7, dorsolateral. 20. South Fork Yuba River, California. Epiproct, lateral, apex." ;
